msg: In libsvn_client diff runners: Move output behaviour booleans that just
trigger wrapping behavior up the call chain. The diff drivers shouldn't
define the output behaviour of the driver.

(diff_wc_wc): Remove show_copies_as_adds and use_git_diff_format which only
change wrapping and ignore ancestry behavior.
(diff_repos_wc): Remove wrap_create, show_copies_as_adds and
use_git_diff_format arguments which only change wrapping behavior.

do_diff_summarize): Update callers.

implementation.
